{"tid":1450510,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[帶風向]我地要認輸先可能會贏","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:40:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T22:03:39.000Z","uid":3003,"like":8,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"37278e1abe876c066f848bcfc7c3a6a343693b44","tid":1450510,"uid":3003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:40:10.000Z","msg":"首先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個post係俾有腦嘅人睇<br />\n無腦嘅直接留言屌柒我推post唔該<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><div style=\"text-align: right;\">順便幫我賺5毛</div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講左個topic先<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>唔好再俾土共有機會入我地做港獨</strong></span><br />\n我知口號係嗌得好爽"},{"pid":"f74728fc5ef4e135ed06625d27f9d1355d4f1d8b","tid":1450510,"uid":3003,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:46:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>首先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個post係俾有腦嘅人睇<br />\n無腦嘅直接留言屌柒我推post唔該<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><div style=\"text-align: right;\">順便幫我賺5毛</div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講左個topic先<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>唔好再俾土共有機會入我地做港獨</strong></span><br />\n我知口號係嗌得好爽</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>唔好再俾土共有機會入我地做港獨</strong></span><br />\n我知口號係嗌得好爽<br />\n但依家個情況係俾土共標籤依場運動做港獨<br />\n而俾佢標籤左係反對緊成個政府<br />\n就已經成為立場問題<br />\n土共只會係度鬧依場運動<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">而唔需要回應</span></strong></span><br />\n咁係對我地係於事無補<br />\n只係成功俾對家用更強硬嘅手段打沉<br />\n而唔係爭取任何野"},{"pid":"9194f5678dc4f9eb4bfd253121c00291e38be4ce","tid":1450510,"uid":290717,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:52:52.000Z","msg":"抗爭由猜疑而起，<br />\n行動亦已經由情緒主勢，<br />\n策略同細節需要耐性處理，<br />\n已經好難實行。<br />\n你應該勸唔到佢地。"},{"pid":"22136b96209d832866dd1c6e43dd4aee8d39fda4","tid":1450510,"uid":3003,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:53:44.000Z","msg":"我地要認嘅係<br />\n以我地嘅力量，我地係無可能同土共鬥<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我地就係順民</strong></span><br />\n俾土民用到對付反動派嘅方法黎搞我地，就只有死路一條<br />\n<br />\n我地要認嘅係，共產黨就係騎住係我地頭上<br />\n<br />\n依家係度講乜最終目標係獨立呀，要反對土共嘅<br />\n都只係好似係度發洩，只係空想<br />\n<br />\n為左啖氣係無可能達到目的<br />\n<br />\n有時要做嘅野，係無咁gur，係難頂，但唔該諗下點先做到我地想要嘅野"},{"pid":"e711c839048ae0bf5d176c48bd00e87a38872fc5","tid":1450510,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:53:58.000Z","msg":"波台狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af99815b8048b0022fa0cef99ebb360acb8afac8","tid":1450510,"uid":119478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:54:59.000Z","msg":"其實未有光復香港時代革命已經比人屈獨"},{"pid":"66c51843707b6d4fce854570b7c5de8f6fd06eac","tid":1450510,"uid":3003,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9194f5678dc4f9eb4bfd253121c00291e38be4ce","tid":1450510,"uid":290717,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:52:52.000Z","msg":"抗爭由猜疑而起，<br />\n行動亦已經由情緒主勢，<br />\n策略同細節需要耐性處理，<br />\n已經好難實行。<br />\n你應該勸唔到佢地。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:55:08.000Z","msg":"我只係睇到訓唔撚著，想打少少野出黎<br />\n都無expect 真係有人會睇"},{"pid":"4e1711c4c8e7bd837e4b38618361a1e2e4ad84b0","tid":1450510,"uid":3003,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:09:12.000Z","msg":"第二<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再嗌反送中</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n土共係未嗌撤回，咁點<br />\n佢係唔再回應，咁點<br />\n<br />\n繼續係依個point爭拗係無意義<br />\n無論覺得土共係咪無正面回應到我地嘅要求<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">事實上土共係唔會再讓步</span></span><br />\n覺得唔滿意，土共都係唔會再理<br />\n佢都係出黎話回應左<br />\n<br />\n而非自己人亦都認為件事已經解決左，無論係其他市民定係外國新聞都係<br />\n<br />\n再拗依個point只會令到我地嘅論據更加薄弱<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咪撚再話民意無撚用<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>無論係民意定輿論對我地都極為緊要</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n因為<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地同對家根本唔平等</span></span><br />\n每一分可能影響到土共嘅因素，我地都要爭<br />\n<br />\n如果剩係發洩嘅，想去打柒班狗嘅，民意緊係無用<br />\n但咁樣只會淪為小學雞爭唔撚過人就去攬炒咁款"},{"pid":"11b55e45f6eba8f95c43f66356f030b8714e6921","tid":1450510,"uid":3003,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e711c839048ae0bf5d176c48bd00e87a38872fc5","tid":1450510,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:53:58.000Z","msg":"波台狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:10:24.000Z","msg":"系，貢典牙"},{"pid":"88c1c6797e371a4646ceadea4535344afe5862c4","tid":1450510,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:13:56.000Z","msg":"唔係想嗌交 但見唔到有咩實際建議"},{"pid":"6d803073c4e734fee567ecf440e7c8c3e4dc4940","tid":1450510,"uid":33749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:14:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80f788abfd66b16f325a6e7cf8a68678c3dc6b0e","tid":1450510,"uid":33749,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:18:38.000Z","msg":"雖然唔係好啱聽<br />\n但係係事實嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7862f1b7822e5c7abfdd29a377b684b0a9f0ca4","tid":1450510,"uid":3003,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:22:18.000Z","msg":"我地企得住陣腳嘅，係追究黑警<br />\n<br />\n班垃圾做嘅野係完全唔合理亦都係痴撚線<br />\n<br />\n而作為公權力，自身帶有咁強烈嘅立場就已經係一個好撚on9同唔應該嘅事<br />\n<br />\n加上佢地嘅行為，就係一班低見識低eq嘅社會垃圾擁有左武力之後自我膨脹嘅舉動<br />\n<br />\n香港警察已經淪為一個流氓機關，用嘅係恐嚇同人治<br />\n<br />\n個感覺就好似無啦啦番左幾十年前咁，就差左無貪污賺到笑<br />\n<br />\n市民對警察失曬信心，先係我地要帶到/要煲嘅topic"},{"pid":"b11674426ee20dd1f3c82d6eaef269458298ab51","tid":1450510,"uid":3003,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"88c1c6797e371a4646ceadea4535344afe5862c4","tid":1450510,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:13:56.000Z","msg":"唔係想嗌交 但見唔到有咩實際建議"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:22:46.000Z","msg":"岩岩先打左一段"},{"pid":"406feb417e55d555603c5f99716ed105751ed621","tid":1450510,"uid":3003,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"80f788abfd66b16f325a6e7cf8a68678c3dc6b0e","tid":1450510,"uid":33749,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:18:38.000Z","msg":"雖然唔係好啱聽<br />\n但係係事實嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:24:30.000Z","msg":"bb miss u<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad56207dfa9061a4dabb9579ee678ec425ac1ee5","tid":1450510,"uid":3003,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"88c1c6797e371a4646ceadea4535344afe5862c4","tid":1450510,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:13:56.000Z","msg":"唔係想嗌交 但見唔到有咩實際建議"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:32:09.000Z","msg":"同埋依家真係無乜可行嘅方法<br />\n<br />\n如果我有，我去做國師啦<br />\n<br />\n但唔代表我地要繼續做啲自我毁滅嘅行為"},{"pid":"547df040f4ca487336027e4555c773234bd58d28","tid":1450510,"uid":103476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:32:58.000Z","msg":"係時候學識反擊啦！非常重要，借位一用<br />\n<br />\n致所有比狗打而想反抗嘅前線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1448193\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1448193</a>"},{"pid":"1e31d65c53c3886eeaa17a31570e0ffd1dbd16d3","tid":1450510,"uid":33749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e1711c4c8e7bd837e4b38618361a1e2e4ad84b0","tid":1450510,"uid":3003,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:09:12.000Z","msg":"第二<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再嗌反送中</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n土共係未嗌撤回，咁點<br />\n佢係唔再回應，咁點<br />\n<br />\n繼續係依個point爭拗係無意義<br />\n無論覺得土共係咪無正面回應到我地嘅要求<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">事實上土共係唔會再讓步</span></span><br />\n覺得唔滿意，土共都係唔會再理<br />\n佢都係出黎話回應左<br />\n<br />\n而非自己人亦都認為件事已經解決左，無論係其他市民定係外國新聞都係<br />\n<br />\n再拗依個point只會令到我地嘅論據更加薄弱<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咪撚再話民意無撚用<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>無論係民意定輿論對我地都極為緊要</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n因為<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地同對家根本唔平等</span></span><br />\n每一分可能影響到土共嘅因素，我地都要爭<br />\n<br />\n如果剩係發洩嘅，想去打柒班狗嘅，民意緊係無用<br />\n但咁樣只會淪為小學雞爭唔撚過人就去攬炒咁款"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:36:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eb472570a4a8223165348e34465a5592d50e041","tid":1450510,"uid":280593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:38:21.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n工業革命"},{"pid":"b388db5f31115b4a0f766237c6bba95cd8926443","tid":1450510,"uid":3003,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"af99815b8048b0022fa0cef99ebb360acb8afac8","tid":1450510,"uid":119478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:54:59.000Z","msg":"其實未有光復香港時代革命已經比人屈獨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:39:01.000Z","msg":"係，依個係土共慣常手段<br />\n一開始提倡本土果陣已經咁做<br />\n處理異己係土共最擅長嘅事<br />\n<br />\n但我依家講嘅就係我地就係要認衰仔<br />\n有必要嘅，我去嗌埋我愛共產黨都仲得<br />\n<br />\n因為力量對比實在太懸殊，我地唔可以俾佢地有更加正當嘅理由去對付我地"},{"pid":"27f4c39547fc1cb1878f436ed545f9d84e2817c6","tid":1450510,"uid":33749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:52:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b18eac57b4861951b5720d4c99017ae537fd357","tid":1450510,"uid":33749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"406feb417e55d555603c5f99716ed105751ed621","tid":1450510,"uid":3003,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"80f788abfd66b16f325a6e7cf8a68678c3dc6b0e","tid":1450510,"uid":33749,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:18:38.000Z","msg":"雖然唔係好啱聽<br />\n但係係事實嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:24:30.000Z","msg":"bb miss u<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:57:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10c770c9d9c671d6f67fb6e6dd327354c2fafdeb","tid":1450510,"uid":299510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:34:39.000Z","msg":"終於有個似樣d嘅po出現<br />\n呢度能夠顧全大局而又唔比情緒支配嘅人太少<br />\n最終只會幫倒忙<br />\n仲隨時推埋跟風嘅人去死"},{"pid":"696098a6163659d8c209f0cc97218ce2f83e0596","tid":1450510,"uid":3003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:05:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43c0d289aeb01461322bbd007f105bc90944a37c","tid":1450510,"uid":3003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27f4c39547fc1cb1878f436ed545f9d84e2817c6","tid":1450510,"uid":33749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:52:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:08:53.000Z","msg":"而我地真係收左手嘅話，只會變到好似大陸人咁，因為已經怕左依個流氓機構，再出黎反對嘅，受到嘅手段係以往嘅集成，會怕佢再對付自已<br />\n到時就成為真真正正嘅順民。。。"}]}